{"tid":2312482,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"班火影撚算唔算係動漫界既芝娃娃？","createTime":"2020-12-05T04:04:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-08T12:27:38.000Z","uid":87394,"like":64,"dislike":81,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"682d6d2c2bbc98286c626b71f96ff07c71f5ffcf","tid":2312482,"uid":87394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T04:04:01.000Z","msg":"明明冇料但又鐘意對人吠撩交嗌<br />\n你話如果係你的名字 哈爾移動城堡呢d三弟四弟出黎駁下嘴我都理解<br />\n又或者op呢d長年龍頭比人破左個紀錄心有不甘我都明<br />\n但班火影撚到底邊到黎既自信學人搭嗲？<br />\n連載期間由頭到尾比op禁撚住黎砌到有心理陰影<br />\n真係得佢地咁唔知醜成日話自己世一，明明就冇野同過個一字扯上關係<br />\n依家個套博人傳佢地自己都嫌三嫌四我都廢事講到咁盡<br />\n成日話鬼滅po煩，人地煩極都係自己講自己<br />\n你地就鐘意拉埋我地新晉動漫一哥落水黎刷存在感又唔覺自己煩<br />\n好心咪咁肉酸啦，係咪自卑到驚唔同我地炎柱比就冇人理你個自來也？"},{"pid":"3bbf3fc4fa5b7f3988bf5ad65c4734bcfa4cd279","tid":2312482,"uid":346404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T04:10:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"372284870d0461fed652deeccf98a0ea79233546","tid":2312482,"uid":166062,"like":18,"dislike":18,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T04:14:09.000Z","msg":"鋼練撚先係<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"126eb8193a392f4b6b061495daaa05eb4663ad18","tid":2312482,"uid":118346,"like":18,"dislike":5,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T04:16:14.000Z","msg":"如果火影今時今日出道，30期都挨唔過就會俾人腰斬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfe85f3a9aedf19ba6fd584f82a9cbcc858adf12","tid":2312482,"uid":365620,"like":41,"dislike":3,"score":38,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T04:16:44.000Z","msg":"真<br />\n唔知做咩要成日攞鬼滅嚟同火影比<br />\n整cheap曬火影"},{"pid":"ff16a97d9ca264bf03920f87bd23711556265dc8","tid":2312482,"uid":52708,"like":44,"dislike":0,"score":44,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-05T04:21:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WV4ZO3q.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWV4ZO3q.gif&h=420c058